name: Black Onyx // (60 g/mol - 2.600)
description:
In ancient times Black Onyx was believed to have a demon imprisoned within that would awake at night, sowing discord, especially between lovers. Strength given from Black Onyx is a protective stone for dark night and lonely places.
Black Onyx holds memories of what happens to the wearer and can be used for psychometry. Effective in past-life work for healing old injuries and physical trauma affecting the present life.
